This project will let you add a train, its destination, frequency and First train time and add it to firebase.
From firebase all the trains in the database will be displayed on the html page in a table
The trains next arrival time and the minutes train is away are calculated and shown in the table
This is the link to the project
https://roopab77.github.io/Train-Scheduler/#

Also update and delete options are available for the user to update or delete any train. On update the firebase is updated the changed info. Also on delete 
the information is deleted on firebase.
